org.apache.openjpa.enhance
Class PCDataGenerator

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.openjpa.enhance.DynamicStorageGenerator
      org.apache.openjpa.enhance.PCDataGenerator
Direct Known Subclasses:
DataCachePCDataGenerator
public class PCDataGenerator
extends DynamicStorageGenerator

Generates PCDataGenerator.DynamicPCData instances which avoid primitive wrappers to optimize memory use and performance at the cost of slightly higher startup time.

Since:
0.3.2
Author:
Steve Kim
